## ğŸ”¹ How HLD and LLD Work Together

They are **sequential, not alternatives**:

**Requirements â†’ HLD â†’ LLD (per service) â†’ Code**

* HLD breaks the system into services
* LLD designs each service internally
* Code implements the LLD

